data.description: Motivated Seller - Welcome to Walden Lake in Plant City! POOL home with a large YARD - over quarter acre! Start planning your outdoor activities and parties now - You are going to love it here. Open layout includes Living Room, Dining Room and Family Room. All Laminate and tiles floors throughout - no carpet! Marvel at the charm of the TWO-sided wood burning fireplace seamlessly connecting the Living Room and Family Room, creating an ambiance of warmth and comfort. Dining Room is ready for those formal dinners and has a generous bay window that bathes the space in natural light. Kitchen offers granite countertops and options for seating with room for barstools and a sunlit breakfast nook. Split bedroom layout. Retreat to the tranquil and large master suite with a spacious walk-in closet and dual sinks in the master bath! Enjoy relaxing OUTSIDE! Extended Lanai with Pavers has room for poolside seating. PLUS you are sure to appreciate the size of this yard! Enjoy the house for YEARS to come with recent upgrades with a new AC (2019) and Roof (2022) and newer appliances. Embrace the Florida lifestyle with this inviting residence. Plant City location puts you near everywhere you need to be with shopping, schools and restaurants close by. Also near I-4 for all your travel needs to Tampa, Lakeland or Orlando. The popular Walden Lake community offers a plethora of amenities, including dog park, playground, sports complex with baseball, volleyball, soccer, tetherball, four square and horseshoes, Pavilion with picnic tables and nature trails with views of the lake and winding trees throughout the community. Experience the epitome of Plant City living – schedule a viewing of this remarkable property and seize the opportunity to call Walden Lake home.
